🎮 Game Management System
The Game Management System is a web-based application designed for efficiently managing games and customers. It provides an intuitive interface for adding, sorting, filtering, and viewing games, as well as managing customer accounts.

📌 Features
🔹 Game Management
Add new games with details such as name, creator, genre, year, quantity, and an image.
Filter games by genre and sort them by name, quantity, or year.
Display all games, including a separate section for sold-out games.
🔹 Customer Management
Add new customers with a username, password, and optional details like name, email, phone, city, and country.
View a list of all registered customers.
🔹 User Interface
Modern, responsive design for seamless user experience.
Theme toggle for switching between light and dark modes.
Dynamic updates using JavaScript and Axios.
🛠️ Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend: Node.js, Express (if applicable)
Database: MongoDB/MySQL (if applicable)
Libraries: Axios (for API requests)

🚀 Installation & Setup
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/game-management-system.git
cd game-management-system
Open index.html in a browser


